Text: Pardon for the intrusion...whoa, what a mess.

Whatever it is I'm looking for, only Eta knows where
it is.
Hey, Eta, are you alive?

Hmm, I feel her presence but I don't see anyone.
Where could she be...?

Could she be here? There's so much experimental
equipment. I just need to work my way through
here and...

Agh...these papers are sure heavy when they're all
piled up...oof. Here goes!
There you are, you're sure working hard.
Hey, are you listening?
Hm?
Looks like you've noticed me.
When did you get here...?

Well, I did try calling out for you like a normal
person would. But it seems you were up to your
usual shenanigans.
What time is it?

It's already lunch time. You didn't show up for
breakfast, so I thought I'd check up on you.
Speaking of which...I am starving.
It astonishes me that you have no concept of time.

Whenever you dive into your research, you withdraw
and put on your scholar's hat.

Whatever hat I have...is normal. And hats don't
have jobs...

I was speaking metaphorically. Try studying some
literature at some point, would you?

I have no need for vague words... It will only make
my reports difficult to comprehend.

Well, I guess that's what makes us different.
Anyway...here, have this.
A sandwich...?

I figure you'd be hungry so I brought leftovers from
this morning's breakfast.

I like...sandwiches. I can eat with one hand...
as I experiment.

True, it's a light meal. I feel you. I do the same
whenever I write.
So, what're you researching now?
Hello?
Guess she's in her own world again.

Hm, I am researching some Shadow Wisdom known
as an "Energy Drink."
Energy Drink...that sounds dangerous.
So this Energy Drink is a drink that gives you...life?

According to Master, it's a drink that can help...
reduce drowsiness, fatigue, and bring out the best
in you.
That sounds amazing. Is it an infusion of herbs?
It's sweet, easy to consume, and bubbly...

It's not your typical bitter-and-hard-to-drink
medicine.

It has an unusual history of being "monstrous,"
"stacked with energy," and "making you fly."
Y-Yeah...stacked with energy, huh...

(If I had one of those Energy Drinks, it would likely
help when I have writer's block...)

If I can make one and drink it...then I can
conduct more research...

(It looks like she's also thinking the same thing.
Now this is some research I can get behind.)
I wonder if it'll really improve your research.

I have developed a theory...I'm presently making
a prototype...
That's great, you're pretty much done.
Yeah, all that's left...is to test it...
What are you looking at me for?
It's just...a test...
Hey, Beta...
Forget it...

Right now I want data on how effective it is with
elves... I'm happy that you, an elf, just happens
to be here...
No...way...no...how.

Tsk...if you insist, guess someone else
will have to do...
Were you just trying to use me as a guinea pig?
They're cute, just like mice...

Don't bother trying to fool me. Either way, you can
forget about using me as a test subject.
Oh well... Another creature will have to do...
